maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Initializing Avatar
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Initialisation Avatar

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: There you are, initialization successful!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Te voilà, Initialisation terminée !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Oh, is the speech synchronization malfunctioning?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Hum, il y a un problème avec la synchronisation de la parole ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: ... Apparently. Well, something just had to go wrong.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: ... Apparemment oui. Il fallait bien que quelque chose aille de travers.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: But you understand me, correct?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Mais tu me comprends, c'est ça ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: [nods]
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: [acquiesce]

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Wait...
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Attends...

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Wha-what is up with your \c[3]level\c[0]?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Qu'est-ce qui se passe avec ton \c[3]niveau\c[0] ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: You are level \c[3]\v[player.level]\c[0].\. It should have been reset.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Tu es niveau \c[3]\v[player.level]\c[0].\. Il aurait dû être remis à un.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Ugh...\. this is not off to a great start.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Eh beh...\. Ça commence bien...

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Ok. We will make it work, somehow.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: OK. On trouvera bien un moyen...

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: You... are probably confused about this situation, correct?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Tu... ne sais pas comment tu t'es retrouvée là, c'est ça ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: [nods]
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: [acquiesce]

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Alright. Let us take small steps.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: C'est bon. On va y aller par petits bouts.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Do you remember VRPs?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Est-ce que tu te souviens des VRPs ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: ...Virtual Ricochet Projectiles?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: ... Virtual Ricochet Projectiles ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: ...Balls?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: ... Les boules ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: [nods]
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: [acquiesce]

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Ok... you seem to remember...
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: OK... tu as l'air de t'en souvenir...

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Carla? We are ready. Please initiate the training sequence.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Carla ? On est prêt. Tu peux démarrer la séquence d'entrainement.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
Press \i[key-throw] to aim.
Release \i[key-throw] to throw.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Appuyez sur \i[key-throw] pour viser.
Relâcher \i[key-throw] pour lancer.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
Use \i[right-stick] to aim.
Press \i[throw] to throw.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Utilisez \i[right-stick] pour viser.
Appuyez sur \i[throw] pour lancer.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Hit enemies with \i[o]
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Frappez les ennemis avec \i[o].

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: VRPs are your most essential tool and weapon.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Les VRPs sont tes outils principaux - et aussi tes armes.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: They are basically like balls.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Ils sont presque comme des boules.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Your task is to hit all these robots with VRPs.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Ton objectif est de toucher tous ces robots avec des VRPs.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
So, give it a shot!\.
Or rather...\.\.\. a throw!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Donc, tire bien !\.
Ou plutôt...\.\.\. lance bien !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Nice work!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Bon travail !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
Well, just to be sure...\.
Let us repeat this exercise with an extended distance.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Bon, juste pour être sûr...\.
On va recommencer avec une distance plus élevée.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Aim and move the cursor towards the edge of the screen to extend your view.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Visez et déplacez le curseur vers le bord de l'écran pour étendre votre champ de vision.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Hit enemies with \i[o].
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Frappez les ennemis avec \i[o].

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Something particular about VRPs: They are not affected by gravity.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Il y a quelque chose de particulier avec les VRPs : Ils ne sont pas affectés par la gravité.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Thus, no matter how far you throw, VRPs will not fall to the ground.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Cela veut dire que peu importe à quelle distance tu les lances, les VRPs ne tombent pas au sol.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Very good.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Très bien.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Ok, next let us enable the Charge Mode.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: OK, ensuite on va activer le Mode Charge.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: \i[tech]Charge Mode
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: \i[tech]Mode Charge

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: You activate charged VRPs by aiming for a longer time.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: En visant plus longtemps, tu peux charger des VRPs.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Let us practice right away.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Essayons ça tout de suite !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
Hit enemies with \i[o]
Avoid enemies with \i[x]
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Frappez les ennemis avec \i[o].
Évitez les ennemis avec \i[x].

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Charge Mode allows for the throwing of larger VRPs.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Le Mode Charge permet de lancer des VRPs plus gros.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Those charged VRPs will ricochet on walls.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Ces VRPs chargés vont rebondir sur les murs.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: That is the reason for their name, you see!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: D'où leur nom !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Using charged VRPs, you can hit the target with the red circle.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Avec des VRPs chargés, tu peux toucher la cible avec le rond rouge.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Easy enough, right?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Aucun problème, n'est-ce pas ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Aim until you see a red line to throw a charged ball.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Visez jusqu'à ce que vous voyez une ligne rouge pour lancer une boule chargée.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Aim precisely to not hit the \i[7] targets
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Visez précisément pour ne pas toucher les cibles \i[7].

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
Hit enemies with \i[6]
Avoid enemies with \i[7]
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Frappez les ennemis avec \i[6].
Évitez les ennemis avec \i[7].

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: ... Well, that was quick...
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: ... Bon, c'était rapide...

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: I suppose I talked too much again.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: J'imagine que j'ai encore trop parlé.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Anyway, enough practice with VRPs.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Peu importe, Ça devrait suffire.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Ok! Enough practice with VRPs.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Bien ! Ça devrait suffire.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: It is about time we put you down on your feet.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Il est temps de te remettre sur tes pieds.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Carla, we are done here. You can terminate the floatation sequence.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Carla, on a fini. Tu peux arrêter la séquence de flottaison.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
Hey there, girl!\.
Welcome to our 
cozy cargo hold!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Salut, beauté !\.
Bienvenue dans notre magnifique soute !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: My name's Carla.\. Nice to meet ya!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Moi c'est Carla.\. Ravie de te rencontrer !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: You sure are a quiet one!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: On dirait que tu es timide ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
Apparently there is an issue with her speech synchronization.\. 
She still understands us, though.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Il y a un problème avec sa synchronisation de la parole.\.
Par contre elle peut nous comprendre.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: No way!\. Is there a way to fix it?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Oh non !\. On peut y faire quelque chose ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: I do not know yet.\. I will have to look into that.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Je ne sais pas encore.\. Il faut que je regarde.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Anyway!\. I'm sure we'll be able to understand each other somehow.\. Non-verbal communication, ya know?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Peu importe !\. Je suis sûr que l'on finira par se comprendre.\. Communication non-verbale et tout ça.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: [nods]
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: [acquiesce]

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Attagirl!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Ouais, comme ça !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Still, kinda would like to know your name.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Mais j'aurais bien voulu connaitre ton nom.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Sergey?\. Can you help us out here?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Sergey ?\. Tu peux nous aider là-dessus ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Right...\. Her name is Lea.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Bien sûr...\. Elle s'appelle Lea.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Lea?\. Well ain't that sweet.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Lea ?\. Si c'est pas chouette.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Well then, Lea, ready to get up?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Bon, alors, Lea, prête à y aller ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: We gotta get you ready for what's coming.\. Ball throwing and the like, ya know?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Il faut qu'on te remette en forme pour la suite.\. Tu sais, le lancer de boules et tout ça.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: And I got just the thing prepared for ya!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Et j'ai déjà tout préparé pour toi !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Follow me!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Suis-moi !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
Press \i[key-up]\i[key-left]\i[key-down]\i[key-right] to move around.
Press  \i[pause] to access the pause menu and save the game.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Déplacez-vous avec \i[key-up]\i[key-left]\i[key-down]\i[key-right].
Appuyez sur \i[pause] pour accéder au menu de pause et sauvegarder votre partie.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
Use \i[left-stick] to move around.
Press  \i[pause] to access the pause menu and save the game.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Déplacez-vous avec \i[left-stick].
Appuyez sur \i[pause] pour accéder au menu de pause et sauvegarder votre partie.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Hey there, Girl! I'd appreciate if you wouldn't step on my stuff like that!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Hé madame ! J'apprécierais si tu grimpais pas sur mes affaires, OK ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Just leave through the door, when you're ready.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Tu es prête ? Alors passe par cette porte.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: [nods]
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: [acquiesce]

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Here we are again.\. Time for you to leave this party.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Et nous revoilà ici.\. Il est temps de se séparer.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: C'mon sweetie, this isn't the time for tearful goodbyes.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Allez chérie, ce n'est pas le moment de s'apitoyer !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Besides, there are those guys.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Et surtout, il y a ces trucs.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig:
Goodbye, Lea.\. 
Enjoy CrossWorlds!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text:
Bonne chance, Lea.\.
Amuse-toi bien dans CrossWorlds !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: To Elevator
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Vers l'Élévateur

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: fr_FR

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Surprise!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Surprise !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: I managed to add a proper \c[3]landmark\c[0] on the cargo ship.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: J'ai réussi à ajouter un vrai \c[3]repère\c[0] sur le porte-conteneur.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: That means from now on you can travel back to the cargo hold whenever you like.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Maintenant tu pourras te téléporter dans les cales quand tu le souhaites.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: But better to not try to drag along other party members.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Mais n'essaie pas de ramener d'autres membres de ton groupe.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: You are the only player that can enter this place.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Tu es la seule joueuse qui peut atteindre cet endroit.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Hey there, girl!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Hé, Chérie !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Hi!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Salut !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: You look pretty well rested.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Tu as l'air de t'être bien reposée.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: I suppose Sergey talked things through with you?
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: J'imagine que Sergey t'as tout expliqué ?

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: [nods]
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: [acquiesce]

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: About time, really.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Il était temps, franchement.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Just so you know, you have all our support!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Sache que l'on sera toujours là pour te soutenir !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: If you ever need a break from that busy Playground, feel free to drop by!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Si jamais tu as b'soin d'une pause en dehors de ce Terrain de jeu bondé, tu peux venir ici !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Well then, let's get you back among all those other players!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Bon alors, allons te ramener auprès de tous ces autres joueurs !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Please stand in the middle of the teleporter.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Si Madame veut bien se placer au centre du téléporteur...

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Everything ready... Good luck over there, girl!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Tout est prêt... Bonne chance là-bas, chérie !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Bye!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Bye !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: There you are!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Ah te voilà !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Hi!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Salut !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: I just wanted to make sure the teleporter still works.
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Je voulais juste vérifier que le téléporteur fonctionnait encore.

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Anyway...
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: En tout cas...

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: I will go ahead, see you there!
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Je vais passer devant, on se voit là-bas !

maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.orig: Meet Sergey, Jet, and the others at \c[3]Cargo Ship - Cabins 2\c[0]
maps/cargo-ship/teleporter.json/entities.text: Rencontrez Sergey, Jet et les autres dans les \c[3]Cabines 2 - \v[area.cargo-ship.name]\c[0]
